games.description:
Get ready for the exciting adventure that awaits you:

• Experience the incredible ragdoll archer physics that will leave you breathless;
• Feel the realistic physics of arrows and armor - each arrow loudly ricochets and bounces, creating unpredictable situations;
• Discover unique arrows with unique gameplay features that will add variety to your game;
• A damage system awaits you, where each part of the body receives a different level of damage, making the game even more realistic;
• Upgrade your hero to become a real master archer;
• Fight interesting opponents and powerful bosses for a real challenge;
• Enjoy beautiful and pleasant graphics, where explosions, sparks and splashes will envelop you like “Fire”;
• Participate in the general ranking of players to show your skills;
• Constantly level up with daily player ratings.
